{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}],"role":"symbol","title":"speed(_:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method","extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore9AnimationV5speedyACSdF","platforms":[{"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"10.15","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"6.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false}],"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"speed"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Double","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sd"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Animation","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore9AnimationV"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"SpeedAnimation.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Animation\/Animation\/SpeedAnimation.swift#L77"}},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Animation\/speed(_:)"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Changes the duration of an animation by adjusting its speed.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/animation\/speed(_:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Animation"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"speed","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"speed","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sd","text":"Double","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore9AnimationV","text":"Animation","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Animation"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"speed","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The speed at which OpenSwiftUI performs the animation."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An animation with the adjusted speed."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Setting the speed of an animation changes the duration of the animation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by a factor of ","type":"text"},{"code":"speed","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". A higher speed value causes a faster animation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sequence due to a shorter duration. For example, a one-second animation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a speed of ","type":"text"},{"code":"2.0","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" completes in half the time (half a second).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["struct ContentView: View {","    @State private var adjustBy = 100.0","","    private var oneSecondAnimation: Animation {","       .easeInOut(duration: 1.0)","    }","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 40) {","            HStack(alignment: .bottom) {","                Capsule()","                    .frame(width: 50, height: 175 - adjustBy)","                Capsule()","                    .frame(width: 50, height: 175 + adjustBy)","            }","            .animation(oneSecondAnimation.speed(2.0), value: adjustBy)","","            Button(\"Animate\") {","                adjustBy *= -1","            }","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Setting "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"speed"},{"type":"text","text":" to a lower number slows the animation, extending its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"duration. For example, a one-second animation with a speed of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0.25"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"takes four seconds to complete."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["struct ContentView: View {","    @State private var adjustBy = 100.0","","    private var oneSecondAnimation: Animation {","       .easeInOut(duration: 1.0)","    }","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 40) {","            HStack(alignment: .bottom) {","                Capsule()","                    .frame(width: 50, height: 175 - adjustBy)","                Capsule()","                    .frame(width: 50, height: 175 + adjustBy)","            }","            .animation(oneSecondAnimation.speed(0.25), value: adjustBy)","","            Button(\"Animate\") {","                adjustBy *= -1","            }","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Declare the user interface and behavior for your app on every platform."}],"url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui","type":"topic","title":"OpenSwiftUI","role":"collection"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Animation/speed(_:)":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Animation\/speed(_:)","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Changes the duration of an animation by adjus